model.name: Bikini Flat Sandal
model.disambiguatingDescription: The Bikini flat sandal is a delicate, feminine design in high-shine rubber. Its slender strap is accessorized with an LV-engraved padlock in gold-tone metal, a precious detail referencing Louis Vuitton leather goods. The strap is adjusted at the back with a small, tonal buckle.
